{
  "name": "RPlog_An_Evening_to_Remember",
  "title": "An Evening to Remember",
  "summary": "Vacationing at the opulent Grand Palanhi Hotel, the Corellian wanderer Paul Nighman dines alone before drifting into the lobby, where he overhears the towering Kasa Horansi warrior Dionysis lecturing the heartbroken young woman Jessalyn about pride, fear, and the celibacy of the Mashi. After Jessalyn flees in tears over her unrequited love for Luke Skywalker, Paul falls into long conversation with Dionysis about Horansi caste culture before seeking Jessalyn out again. He spends the evening gently counseling the despondent Jessalyn, urging her to value herself and to prove she need not be a liability to the man she loves. Their talk is interrupted when a grief-stricken Luke staggers through, mourning the death of his friend Erik, and drops his lightsaber in the square. Jessalyn retrieves the saber and follows Luke to comfort him, leaving Paul to return alone to the lobby with his book.",
